short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dominate the battlefield every time you open a new tab with the intense visuals of Call of Duty: Warzone Live Wallpaper 🎮💥🪖

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into the high-stakes action of Call of Duty: Warzone, where survival is everything and strategy meets chaos. This live wallpaper brings the heart-pounding energy of Verdansk and Al Mazrah to your browser, with dynamic imagery of your favorite operatives, stunning landscapes, and explosive combat moments. Whether you’re a solo fighter or part of a squad, this extension is the ultimate tribute to Warzone’s adrenaline-packed gameplay.

Key Features
🎮 Dynamic Live Wallpaper: Immerse yourself in the iconic battlefields of Call of Duty: Warzone.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Explore the web with a tactical edge, right from your Warzone-themed tab.
🕒 Clock & Date Display: Stay sharp and on time for your next match.
🔗 Customizable Shortcuts: Access your go-to sites with just a click.
🔗 Extension Management Links: Manage or explore extensions with the options at the lower-left corner.
Gear up and take on the world with the Call of Duty: Warzone Live Wallpaper—perfect for players who live for the thrill of the drop zone and the glory of the win!
